sourcesContent: import React, { useEffect, useState } from 'react' import { Box, Button, Grid, Typography, Card, FormControl, FormHelperText, InputLabel, Select, MenuItem, IconButton, CircularProgress, Stack, TextField } from '@mui/material'; import { ItemAnimation } from '../components/ItemAnimation' import PirelliIcon from '../images/Logo_Pirelli.png' import { StaticDateTimePicker } from '@mui/x-date-pickers/StaticDateTimePicker'; function MainPage() { const [startDate, setStartDate] = useState(dayjs('2022-04-17T15:30')) const [endDate, setEndDate] = useState(dayjs('2022-04-17T15:30')) function getMetrics(){ console.log("start date=", startDate, " - end date=", endDate) } return ( Clara BOT {setStartDate(event.target.value)}}/> {setEndDate(event.target.value)}}/> ) } export default MainPage;
